00:04:30.980 --> 00:04:32.240

type in your domain name.



63

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:35.100

Let me be the first to congratulate you.



64

00:04:35.100 --> 00:04:38.420

You literally have a live website up and running now.



65

00:04:38.930 --> 00:04:39.860

It's not much yet.



66

