And now it's time to customize it.



68

00:04:45.590 --> 00:04:49.850

Now that your website is up and running, there are a few basic settings you'll want to customize to



69

00:04:49.850 --> 00:04:50.420

your liking.



70

00:04:50.930 --> 00:04:55.310

So from your WordPress dashboard, click General under the Settings menu.



71

00:04:55.880 --> 00:04:58.030

On this page, you can change your site title.



72

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:00.830

You'll notice there's probably a default placeholder there.



73

00:05:01.130 --> 00:05:04.700

Just clear that out and enter whatever you want your site to be called.



74

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:09.710

Then you can add a short tagline, which may show up in various places on your site.



75

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:11.000

This is optional.



76

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:13.580

You can just delete the placeholder text if you're unsure.



77

00:05:14.650 --> 00:05:19.180

Finally, be sure to set the time zone to match your local time when you're happy with these settings,



78

